    <stitle>2 SPEED AND DOUBLE REDUCTION SINGLE DRIVE AXLES: EATON - ADJUST/INSTALL - FINAL PINION BEARING PRELOAD
        TEST
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc id="hl1401606" svcproctype="test" graphiccount="0">
        <title>FINAL PINION BEARING PRELOAD TEST</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">With pinion and bearing cage assembled as previously described, mount the assembly in a
                press equipped with a calibrated load cell to insure proper clamp load. Position a sleeve so that load
                is applied directly to backface of the outer bearing cone. Apply a clamp load (refer to
                <hotlnk xrefid="hl1401607">Table 2</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
